  <text corresp="#DEd" xml:lang="sa">
    <body>
      <p xml:id="Kk1.0.1-8">
        <pb n="98"/><lb n="7"/>[ayaṃ heturūpako 'laṃkāraḥ | tad yathā ‘gāmbhīryeṇa] <note xml:lang="en">R2a1</note> samudro 'si’ <note>kāvyādarśa <lb n="8"/><num xml:lang="en">2.85</num></note> iti | tasyāgādhatvaṃ yathoktaguṇavattayātulatvam | ‘duḥkhainovyasaneṣv agham’ ity a<lb n="9"/>bhidhānād anaghaguṇatvaṃ sukhahetulaghutvavispaṣṭatvādi | sevā śrutacintāvyākhyānādiḥ | <lb n="10"/>akṣayatvaṃ saṃpūrṇatā | sarvanāmaśabdaiḥ prakrāntasya liṅgam ādīyate prakāśyamānasya vā | <lb n="11"/>tad yathā ‘karmaṇā yam abhipraiti sa saṃpradānam’ <note>pā. <num xml:lang="en">1.4.32</num></note>, ‘aṇau yat_ karma ṇau cet_ sa <lb n="12"/>kartā’ | tad atra kāmacārāc chrutatvāc ca prakrāntasyaiva sindhuśabdasya liṅgena sa iti <lb n="13"/>nirdeśo na nāmaliṅgānuśāsanaśabdasya | śrīs trivargasaṃpattiḥ | tad uktaṃ vyāḍinā
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="Kk1.0.1-9">
       <l><lb n="14"/>lakṣmīsarasvatīdhītrivargasampad_vibhūtiśobhāsu |</l>
       <l><lb n="15"/>upakaraṇaveśaracanāvidhāsu ca śrīr iti prathitā ||</l>
       <trailer><lb n="16"/>iti |</trailer>
      </lg>
      <p xml:id="Kk1.0.1-10">athavā yā vāṅ_mayasarvajñatvalakṣaṇā svārthasaṃpat, yā ca taddhetukā trivargahetuḥ <lb n="17"/>parārthasaṃpat_ tadubhayī śrīḥ | svaparārthasaṃpadā ca puṇyajñānasaṃbhārād_ <app><lem>yatnāt_ prāpto</lem><rdg wit="#R">ayatnāyāto</rdg></app> mokṣo <lb n="18"/>'mṛtam iti |
      </p>
    </body>
